com.ubercab.autodispose.rxlifecycle

Class RxLifecycleInterop

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ubercab.autodispose.rxlifecycle.RxLifecycleInterop

  • public final class RxLifecycleInterop
extends java.lang.Object
    Interop for RxLifecycle. This provides static factory methods to convert LifecycleProviders into ScopeProvider representations. Note: RxLifecycle treats the OutsideLifecycleException as normal terminal event. In such cases the stream is just disposed.
